Secret::Simple version 0.10

This module implements a straightforward interface for encrypting and
decrypting secret information like user IDs and passwords. Use is
primarily geared towards accessing or embedding secure credentials from
or within Perl code and configuration files (e.g. database connection
or remote account credentials), but in can also be used to encrypt
arbitrary data. See the POD documentation for more details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Carp
    Crypt::CBC
    Crypt::Rijndael_PP
    MIME::Base64

